doctype html
html
    head
        meta(name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow")
        title= title
    style.
        body{
            -moz-user-select: none;
            -webkit-user-select: none;
            -ms-user-select: none;
            user-select: none;
            -o-user-select: none;
            background-color: #ededed;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #535353;
        }

        li {
            color: #272727;
            margin-top:4px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            margin-top: 25px;
            margin-left:5px;
            margin-right:5px;
            padding-left: 16px;
            padding-right: 16px;
            padding-top: 5px;
            padding-bottom:5px;
            box-shadow: 0px 1px 3px #9c9c9c;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }
        .last-card{
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

    body
        .card
            h2.title Version 11.2.3
            ul
                li <b>Fast Conversion Mode: </b> Now convert mp3 audio 3 times faster. Switch mode from settings. (Only for arm CPU architecture)
                li Insufficient storage bug fixed.
                li Minor bug fixes.

        .card
            h2.title Version 11.2.2
            ul
                li <b>SD CARD ISSUE RESOLVED!!</b> Any folder in external SD card can be selected as a download location
                li Support for 480p, 1080p and 4k Video Preview
                li <b>Download Manager: </b> Now download any file from anywhere using Videoder Fast Multithread downloader
                li Auto Resume Downloads on network interruptions
                li Option to download only over WiFi network
                li Audio plugin size reduced by 80%
                li Download maximum mp3 quality audio from Quick and MultiSelection download.
                li Missing 60fps resolutions bug fixed
                li New share format from youtube app support
                li UI Enhancements and Bug Fixes

        .card
            h2.title Version 11.1
            ul
                li Fast download mode (Multi Thread 10X faster Downloading)
                li Convert any video to mp3
                li Preview videos in 144p to 720p resolutions
                li More beautiful themes added.
                li More resolutions supported. (8k, M4a, Mp3 in different qualities)
                li Recommended videos with auto play feature.
                li Drag and Select multiple options in search/playlist and download them in a go.

        .card
            h2.title Version 11.0
            ul
                li Download 4k and 60fps videos.
                li In built web browser.
                li Explore trending videos.
                li Playlist and channel downloading.
                li Detailed info of every video (view count, likes, dislikes, description, subscribers, upload date, etc)

        .card
            h2.title Version 10.0
            ul
                li UI updated with the latest material design.
                li Select multiple videos and download them in one go.
                li Quick download option which lets you download anything in a second.
                li Age restriction bug solved. (Sign in to watch and download restricted videos)

        .card
            h2.title Version 6.0
            ul
                li Download videos upto 1080p (full HD) resolutions.
                li Download unlimited music (mp3 also available)
                li A much enhanced user interface.
                li More detailed settings screen.
                li Auto correct misspelled searches.

        .card
            h2.title Version 4.0
            ul
                li A new UI with a beautiful white theme.
                li A very useful help section.
                li Preview any video before downloading.


        .card.last-card
            h2.title Version 1.0
            ul
                li Search videos from around the world
                li Download unlimited Videos in HD, SD, LD definitions in various formats like flv, mp4 and webm
                li Download any video in just two steps.
                li Sleek interface and design.
